name: Susanna Quinn
description: Susanna Quinn, better known asSusie "Q", is a character featured inCyberpunk 2077. Susie "Q" is the leader of theMoxes, a gang of joytoys devoted to "protecting working boys and girls". She runsLizzie's Bar, the gang's main base of operations. Susie takes a different approach to the Mox's leadership, prioritizing the gang's business interests over its history of protecting the vulnerable. She insists the gang's role as protectors and activists is in the past. However, this view is not shared by all of the Mox, with those such asJudy √Ålvarezcontinuing to give help to those in need.
